CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FPolice budgets for technology have
OL,8,Ffallen to half the level of other
OL,9,Fpublic bodies amid too much political
OL,10,Ffocus on officer numbers, the head of
OL,11,FBritain's biggest force will say.
OL,13,FSir Mark Rowley will use a speech in
OL,14,FLondon on Wednesday to call for police
OL,15,Fchiefs to be given more freedom to use
OL,16,Fnew technology and not have to wait
OL,17,Ffor legislation to keep up.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
