FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police chief will
OL,8,Fhighlight plans including the
OL,9,Fexpansion of live facial recognition
OL,10,Fand drone coverage for every London
OL,11,Fborough, as well as increasing use of
OL,12,FAI.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, human rights campaign
OL,15,Fgroup Liberty said there should be a
OL,16,Flegal framework in place before the
OL,17,Fforce increases its use of static live
OL,18,Ffacial recognition cameras.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FBut Sir Mark is set to argue that it
OL,8,Fis not viable for forces to wait for a
OL,9,Fseparate legal framework for each new
OL,10,Fdevelopment in technology.
OL,12,FHe is expected to say: "Policing by
OL,13,Fconsent is key to the British policing
OL,14,Fmodel and is something we must
OL,15,Ftreasure.
OL,26,@tD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,F"However, when it comes to new
OL,8,Ftechnologies, as we saw with Live
OL,9,FFacial Recognition, some campaign
OL,10,Fgroups call for new legislation and
OL,11,Frestrictions every time a new
OL,12,Fcapability emerges.
OL,14,F"While that comes from a legitimate
OL,15,Fplace, it risks slowing progress to
OL,16,Fthe point where policing cannot keep
OL,17,Fpace with the threats we face.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,F"We already operate within a complex
OL,8,Flegislative framework including the
OL,9,FHuman Rights Act, the Investigatory
OL,10,FPowers Act, the Data Protection Act
OL,11,Fand GDPR, and are overseen by multiple
OL,12,Fregulators and commissioners.
OL,14,F"If every time a new capability
OL,15,Femerges, or we find a new use case for
OL,16,Fdata exploitation, we have to wait for
OL,17,Fnew legislation before we use it, we
OL,18,Fwill fail.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,F"We cannot legislate for every
OL,8,Fincremental development in technology.
OL,9,FThe pace is simply too fast, and the
OL,10,Flegislative process is too slow."
OL,12,FHe will argue that the Met is able to
OL,13,Fspend around #6,000 per person on data
OL,14,Fand technology, while other public
OL,15,Fbodies can spend around #13,000.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FSir Mark will say: "For decades,
OL,8,Fpolitical debate has focused heavily
OL,9,Fon police officer numbers, with far
OL,10,Fless attention given to whether
OL,11,Fpolicing has the tools it needs to do
OL,12,Fthe job effectively."
OL,14,FThe force is planning to have drone
OL,15,Fcoverage in every London borough by
OL,16,Fthis time next year, and to establish
OL,17,Fa network with the other emergency
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FThe Met currently has three drone
OL,8,Fsites, with a total of nine devices
OL,9,Fdeploying to around 200 incidents per
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,FA national scheme to use drones as
OL,13,Ffirst responders has seen pilot
OL,14,Fschemes take place over the past two
OL,15,Fyears, including in Norfolk, which has
OL,16,Flimited access to the helicopters
OL,17,Fflown by the National Police Air
OL,18,FService because they are stationed so
OL,19,Ffar away.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FThe idea is that forces can send
OL,8,Fremotely operated drones to the scene
OL,9,Fof incidents to gather information
OL,10,Fmore quickly about what has happened
OL,11,Fand what resources they need to send,
OL,12,Fas well as for things like tracking
OL,13,Fsuspects.
OL,15,FThe Met's trial began in October last
OL,16,Fyear, with drones placed in Islington,
OL,17,Fthe West End and Hyde Park.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FSir Mark will say: "This is a turning
OL,8,Fpoint for policing in London. Today we
OL,9,Fare setting out how we will
OL,10,Fsignificantly step up our use of
OL,11,Ftechnology to fundamentally change how
OL,12,Fwe protect the public.
OL,14,F"Drones are already transforming how
OL,15,Fwe respond to incidents ` getting
OL,16,Fvisuals from the scene in minutes,
OL,17,Fgiving officers critical intelligence
OL,18,Fand helping us act faster and more
OL,19,Fsafely.
OL,26,@oD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1782328696
OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,F"Now we are scaling that capability
OL,8,Facross London and working with
OL,9,Fpartners to create a truly integrated,
OL,10,Fcity-wide drone network.
OL,12,F"But this is about more than
OL,13,Findividual tools. Criminals are
OL,14,Falready using technology to become
OL,15,Fmore organised, more connected and
OL,16,Fharder to catch.
OL,18,F"Right now, policing is trying to keep
OL,19,Fup using systems that are too slow and
OL,20,Ftoo restrictive. If that does not
OL,21,Fchange, we won't succeed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
