OL,3,CMet plans to increase live facial
OL,4,Crecognition and drones in every London
OL,5,Cborough
OL,7,FOfficers have also used AI to trawl
OL,8,Fthrough CCTV footage, which the Met
OL,9,Fclaims has saved hundreds of hours of
OL,10,Finvestigators' time.
